Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:25.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:55.14,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:48.73,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:58.74,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:01.46,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you proceed now that things have taken a turn for the worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fate that awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a storybook vision of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Heaven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuckin' bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed me here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Namatame Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the ones I saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This dude high or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Nanako back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You put the people you saw on the Midnight Channel into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On rainy nights... on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they signal me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't put you in the TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you have ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that we wouldn't have been able to face ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we nearly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's completely lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! "Save," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just killing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you plan on killing this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a {\i1}savior!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,H-His power is attracting more and more Shadows to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, I'm going to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will... I will save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My body...{is moving on its own!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?{SAY IT SAY IT SAY IT}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, run!{I MIGHT START RAPING YOU.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is controlling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Who knew this guy would be such a pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's charging up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can take us out in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I won't let anyone get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!{oh hey, it stopped.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, don't fight with them.{BY THE POWER OF LOLI I COMMAND YOU}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shi—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is...{MOVING ON ITS OWN, RIGHT????}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...moving...{SAY IT. SAY IT.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...on its own!{FUCK YEA!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to save that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, please save Nanako!{AHHHH GHOST HAND}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohryu?!{ultimate hierophant persona? omg}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough!{they're making naoto's persona seem useful}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Shadows are going bear-serk!{Oh, shout out to that one guy on /a/}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rawr!{Who is using that subtitle renderer that displays comments}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako? Nanako!{You really should get a better media player}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's must be in pain, but she doesn't seem to be injured anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This place must not be good for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to carry her out, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,still hasn't recovered from her cold.{... FUCKING JAPAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to go through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana's still so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so her other self didn't appear like it did for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And she got caught in all that craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All those Shadows just had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she could've handled that, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I waste time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,listening to what Namatame had to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't tried to engage him in conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd rescued Nanako immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, it isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i}is{\i0} my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I prioritized solving the case over Nanako's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, Nanako is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,enough of this pity party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is feeling pathetic and consoling each other gonna solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you desperately trying to save Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys. Acting all gloomy won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Think how Nanako would feel if she saw us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, you were pretty cool for once, Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, don't make a scene in the hospital. Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the fog especially thick today?{so's my dick}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it's really cold, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out. It's about Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he regained consciousness this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"According to the police interrogation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,he confessed that he regrets what he did and admits that he was just scared."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So he admitted to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I received word from the hospital this morning that it's okay to visit Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should go see her when school lets out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Nanako's doing a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.{CHRISTIAN PROPAGANDA}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where's Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to invite her too, but she wasn't in her classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nanako's doing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just having a hard time believing that the case is truly over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're a unique person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You referred to me as your friend, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you said at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad you were there."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted someone to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was trying so desperately to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take away my ability as a detective, I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said you were happy that I was there. {typo in stream}{thank you for leaving it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me a place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're headed for the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, weren't we going to see Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still just lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, y-you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. She isn't able to talk a lot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, you came here again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you're worried about your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but you still need your rest, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll wheel him back to his room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing, Adachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, that's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,About Namatame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still mentally unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're slowly piecing together his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything new?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is still a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess it's okay to tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There were entries about Ms. Yamano and Ms. Konishi in the diary we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Namatame had been making advances on Ms. Konishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We think that could be connected to why he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bottle it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame's been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't hurt anyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think Nanako can go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima's still hospitalized, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder what's up with this fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a person whose child has been bedridden because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's really poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Evacuate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is poisonous gas! It's loaded with viruses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if you breathe this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him? What a creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The idea that this fog is poisonous is just plain stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that was an extreme example,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that people are getting increasingly worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People everywhere are talking about the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very unusual for fog to last this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Visibility's so bad, it's kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean in the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guys, put on your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,These glasses are meant to help us see through the fog in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But putting that aside, no glasses would improve one's visibility in a fog under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the fog from over there be leaking into our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys think that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It just popped into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the fog from the TV world really be leaking into our world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It does seem a lot like the fog on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but beyond that, I'm clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the case against Namatame hasn't been going well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,they haven't made any progress with Namatame's interrogations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's still confined to his hospital bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so further interrogation has yet to commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog isn't leaving, and the interrogation isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We solved the case, but I still feel bummed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I still stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept your promise to help me find the person who was disrupting the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should be going back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't wanna go until Nana gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do we have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should move in with you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Being together would really heat things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it {\i1}has{\i0} been unusually cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you promised Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I promised that we'd go buy a space heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're getting a space heater, we'd better get some oranges to complete the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji, what'd you buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Nanako and I could make some knitted animals when she gets better,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we pick out a Christmas present for Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The space heater isn't good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, as soon as Nanako's out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how about we have a party at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A party? That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And we'll bake the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1149,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1360.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(429,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1467,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.5,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1588.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,1035)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(51,1036.5)}Of co
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1852.5,1035)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you're not! Are you {\i1}trying{\i0} to send Nanako back to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is {dog}Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Keep calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a sudden change in Nanako's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry over to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I even looked at some space heaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy one together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make snowmen when it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised that we'd play together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How come he's the one who gets to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We must... reach out to the truth.
